Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.40,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}視界奪う憂鬱を　優雅にさばいて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:54.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ほらBreakfast
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:57.37,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ナイフ＆フォークで平らげる　All  Right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:00:59.37,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いざなえ　Gracefulなlife
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.70,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無頼　無粋　野暮はNo Thanx
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ハートは激アツ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.29,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}振る舞いは　Cool　Cooler　Coolest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.71,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曲げんな　Get　Up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:09.38,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}半端　軟派　猫背はNo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.92,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}激流にさえ　立ち向かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:14.30,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}流れ　逆らえ　涼しげなフェスで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:18.51,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}苦難は日々を飾る花束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:22.10,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}踊れ　独りでも　ステージの上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.02,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幕上がり　沸くオーディエンス
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:27.19,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さあIt's　Show　Time!　見開いて逸らすな目を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:30.06,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}眩しく孤高のニューワールド
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:33.44,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah　Yeah　ブレるな　Hey　Boys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:36.32,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あふれ出す　想い　己つらぬけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:38.53,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}スペシャルをプレゼント
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:41.41,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行こうぜ　Go!　ありのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:43.54,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Break　Out!  嵐起こせ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:46.54,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おもてなす　お前連れてく　HEAVENへ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.79,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Wake  Up!  弱き者よ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:52.50,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はみ出せ　Hey!  空気なんて読むなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.88,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}檻破れ　お前のスタイル押し通せ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.26,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ah  Virtuous  knight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.22,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}共に行こう　Hey  Girl
